# Example profile's toolchain additions — merged with base.list via the union of
# /opt/toolchain/tools.d/*.list. Columns per base.list: <source> <command> [agent note].
# A row with no note is installed but NOT advertised to the agent (opt-in context).
# More illustration-of-the-add-pattern than necessity — trim or extend freely.

# Advertised to the agent (carry a note):
ast-grep    ast-grep  structural, syntax-aware code search & rewrite
gron        gron      flatten JSON to greppable lines (gron|rg; gron -u reverses)
yq          yq        query/edit YAML, JSON, TOML

# Installed for interactive (human) use, not advertised (no note):
claude      claude
bat         bat
pipx:icdiff icdiff
